latestIgtvVideos.title: Skin Care Regime🧼🧖🏻‍♀️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hello My Darlings! Since festive season just around the corner, I thought why not to share my Skin Care Regime with you! Thanks to Skin Talk (@skintalk_skincare ) for sending me their exclusive Rose and Beetroot Face Pack. As we know beetroot and rose itself is a healthy combination, I thought why not to use it with Curd to include more suppleness to my skin. Here's what I noticed post using this Facepack :- 

𝐈𝐭 𝐆𝐚𝐯𝐞 𝐦𝐞 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐒𝐤𝐢𝐧
𝐆𝐚𝐯𝐞 𝐚 𝐃𝐞𝐭𝐨𝐱 𝐭𝐨 𝐦𝐲 𝐒𝐤𝐢𝐧
𝐑𝐞𝐩𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐢𝐬𝐡 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐝𝐞𝐚𝐝 𝐒𝐤𝐢𝐧 𝐓𝐞𝐱𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞

I totally loved it! Thanks to @skintalk_skincare 

After using the facepack, I always make sure to hydrate my face with a mist for a natural hydration, Here I used Innisfree Tea Trea Face mist @innisfreeindia 

Last, but not the least; Always apply a serum, Here I used @milagro.beauty in the end since it balance the skin texture and suppleness whilst leaving a natural glow. 

Happy Skin Care This Festive Season!❤️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Lip Hack💄💄
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Lip hack for your every day go to occasion! Make your lip color long lasting and pigmented with this amazing lip hack💓💄 Follow these simple steps - Apply a lip balm on your lips thoroughly and leave it for 1 min so that it gets absorbed by lips.
- Take a fresh toothbrush and exfoliate your lips which will dread off all the dead skin. - Use your concealer on the exfoliated lips
- Use your favourite lip pencil on the top of your lips
- Apply some loose powder over it. - Apply your favourite lip gloss on top of it and here you go!👄💄
